  "remarks": "Rukhservomotor LLC is a Belarusian company which focuses on the development and manufacturing of precision coordinate systems. It supplies companies which are military end-users with goods with military end-use. The company participates in the production of panoramic sights (PKP) for Russian T-72 and T-90 tanks.",
